                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! We work with clients across the country. While we're based in Boulder, Colorado, we can collaborate effectively through video calls, email, and collaborative tools to serve clients anywhere.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

